short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Nature Extension is designed to bring a beautiful calming nature images to your every day peripheral.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Now your first browser page will no longer be a boring search bar but your new extension will bring you the joy and calm of nature's landscapes. 

Once installed you are able to customize the Nature Tab by choosing your preferred background from one of the many nature settings in our image library. 

You are also able to view your local time and local weather. 

We hope you enjoy using the Nature Tab as much as we have.
